From 4a4a1bb0a5176fdf3e0787d1f82287c0aa65d7f2 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Claude Code <claude@anthropic.com>
Date: Fri, 10 Apr 2026 08:01:21 +0000
Subject: [PATCH 2/5] Update QJson includes for Qt4 compatibility
MIME-Version: 1.0
Content-Type: text/plain; charset=UTF-8
Content-Transfer-Encoding: 8bit

Change QJson includes to use .h extension for qjson4 library:
- #include <QJsonDocument> → #include <QJsonDocument.h>
- #include <QJsonObject> → #include <QJsonObject.h>
- #include <QJsonArray> → #include <QJsonArray.h>
- #include <QJsonValue> → #include <QJsonValue.h>
- #include <QJsonParseError> → #include <QJsonParseError.h>

Affects 66 files across api_responses, types, frontend-common, and GUI.
